---
// src/components/AccountantsSection.astro

// Removemos a importação do lucide-react e usaremos ícones SVG diretamente
---

<section class="py-24 px-4 bg-slate-950 relative overflow-hidden">
  {/* Background Effects - Atualizado conforme PlansSection */}
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-950/30 via-transparent to-orange-950/30"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
    
    {/* Header com destaque especial */}
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-yellow-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/30 rounded-full px-6 py-3 mb-8">
        {/* Ícone Crown SVG */}
        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="text-sm font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-200 to-yellow-200 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Oportunidade Exclusiva
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
        <span class="text-white">Contador,</span>
        <br />
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 via-yellow-400 to-orange-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          torne-se um Agente Integrativo Tucont
        </span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-orange-200 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Transforme sua prática contábil em um <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-400">negócio estratégico</span> 
        com nossa tecnologia, metodologia e suporte completo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center mb-16">
      
      {/* Conteúdo à esquerda */}
      <div class="space-y-8">
        
        {/* Benefícios principais */}
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="group flex gap-4 p-6 bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-500/10 hover:border-orange-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              {/* Ícone Crown SVG */}
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Plataforma com IA e método exclusivo</h3>
              <p class="text-orange-200 leading-relaxed">Acesso a tecnologia proprietária e frameworks validados em milhares de empresas</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group flex gap-4 p-6 bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-500/10 hover:border-orange-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              {/* Ícone Shield SVG */}
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Autonomia com suporte</h3>
              <p class="text-orange-200 leading-relaxed">Trabalhe de forma independente com backup completo da nossa equipe especializada</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="group flex gap-4 p-6 bg-slate-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-500/20 rounded-2xl hover:bg-orange-500/10 hover:border-orange-500/40 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-300">
              {/* Ícone TrendingUp SVG */}
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Expansão com marca consolidada</h3>
              <p class="text-orange-200 leading-relaxed">Cresça aproveitando nossa reputação e metodologia reconhecida no mercado</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* CTA Principal */}
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <a 
            href="https://wa.me/5511999999999?text=Quero ser um Agente Integrativo Tucont - Conte-me mais sobre a parceria"
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full md:w-auto bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-yellow-500 hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-yellow-600 text-slate-900 px-10 py-5 text-xl font-bold rounded-2xl shadow-2xl transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-300"
          >
            {/* Ícone Users SVG */}
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
            </svg>
            Quero ser parceiro
            {/* Ícone ArrowRight SVG */}
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 ml-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
          
          <p class="text-orange-300 text-sm">
            Processo seletivo • Vagas limitadas • Suporte total
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>

      {/* Imagem/Visual à direita */}
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-yellow-500/20 backdrop-blur-sm border border-orange-400/30 rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-2xl shadow-orange-500/10">
          <div class="aspect-video bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-900/50 to-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/src/images/page/partner.png"
              alt="Plataforma SpeedCont - Gestão contábil profissional"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
            />
          </div>
          
          {/* Stats overlay */}
          <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-slate-900/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-4">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-400">300%</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-300">Aumento médio de receita</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-400">24h</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-300">Suporte especializado</div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-orange-400">100+</div>
                <div class="text-xs text-slate-300">Agentes ativos</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    {/* Seção de destaque final */}
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-900/30 to-yellow-900/30 backdrop-blur-xl border border-orange-500/30 rounded-3xl p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
          Transforme sua contabilidade tradicional em consultoria estratégica
        </h3>
        <p class="text-orange-200 mb-6 text-lg">
          Junte-se aos contadores que já descobriram como <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-400">triplicar a receita</span> oferecendo valor real aos clientes.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            {/* Ícone Sparkles SVG */}
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Tecnologia exclusiva</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            {/* Ícone Target SVG */}
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Métodos validados</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-2">
            {/* Ícone Zap SVG */}
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm text-slate-300">Resultados garantidos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>